################################################################################
#
#  SSMODELS /src/ directory
#
#  *  /ssmodels/
#     Contains the 'ssmodels' R package. Should _NOT_ be modified unless you
#     Know What You Are Doing (TM). Has an internal git repository to allow
#     versioning.
#
#     To build and deploy a new version, from the command line in the /ssmodels/
#     directory type:
#
#     > R CMD build src
#     > R CMD INSTALL ssmodels_0.1-0.tar.gz
#
#     To generate a pdf ssmodels package document, from the command line in the
#     /src/ directtory type:
#
#     > R CMD Rd2pdf src
#
#     where you have replaced "0.0-1" with the latest version number.
#
################################################################################
